## 2026-04-04 - variableSync.ts O(n) sequential async calls and stale variable cache
- **`readFigmaVariables`**: replaced O(vars×modes) sequential `getVariableByIdAsync` calls with a single `Promise.all([getLocalVariableCollectionsAsync, getLocalVariablesAsync])` + a `Map<id, Variable>` for O(1) lookup per varId.
- **`deleteOrphanVariables`**: same fix — replaced sequential `getVariableByIdAsync` per varId with a single `getLocalVariablesAsync` + Map lookup; parallelized the two top-level fetches with `Promise.all`.
- **`applyVariables` stale cache**: after `createVariable`, push the new `Variable` into `localVariables` so subsequent `findVariableInList` calls (same sync loop) can find just-created entries and avoid duplicate creation.

